Title: Fingine: Thoughts on Side Projects and Financial Simulation
Description: One ambition of mine is to retire relatively early (around 55) and in the period prior to that to take jobs without consideration for their financial compensation. To achieve that, I pay attention to how my net worth, savings rate, and investments track with my goals using the coast FIRE calculator.
